---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Affiliate Disclosure" description="Full affiliate disclosure for FieldHealth Africa — how affiliate relationships work, what we recommend, and what we will never recommend.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20">
    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-white mb-4">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-8 text-white/65 text-sm leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">What this means</h2>
        <p>Some links on FieldHealth Africa — particularly on the <a href="/picks" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">Picks page</a> and in blog posts — are affiliate links. When you click one of these links and make a purchase, FieldHealth Africa earns a small commission from the merchant. <strong class="text-white">This costs you nothing extra.</strong></p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">Our recommendation policy</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">We only recommend tools that Dr. Fomukong has personally used in an operational health setting or in building FieldHealth Africa. Affiliate relationships are never the reason a tool is recommended — they are set up after we have already decided a tool is worth recommending.</p>
        <p>All affiliate links are identified with a disclosure line immediately below the recommendation card.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">What we will never recommend</h2>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-red-500/[0.05] border border-red-500/20 p-5 text-red-200/70">
          <p class="font-semibold text-red-300 mb-2">Non-negotiable ethical constraint</p>
          <p>FieldHealth Africa will never carry affiliate relationships for: clinical decision-support software, drug suppliers, laboratory suppliers, diagnostic tools, or any product whose misuse could affect individual patient outcomes. Our affiliate programme covers only productivity tools, data and analysis software, and learning platforms.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">Cloaked links</h2>
        <p>Affiliate links on this site go through <code class="text-cyan-300 bg-white/[0.06] px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">fieldhealthafrica.org/recommends/[slug]</code>. This is standard practice — it keeps URLs clean, allows us to update destination URLs without editing every page, and lets us understand which recommendations resonate. We do not sell or share this data.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-white mb-3">Questions</h2>
        <p>Email <a href="mailto:hello@fieldhealthafrica.org" class="text-cyan-400 underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors">hello@fieldhealthafrica.org</a> with any questions about our affiliate relationships.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
